title: Ep. - 263 - HANNAH FERRIER FROM BELOW DECK
description:
Hannah Ferrier from Below Deck gives the scoop about her pregnancy and this season of the Bravo series.

 

Podcast host Jess Rothschild helps Kate review the Amazon documentary Kumare, which follows American filmmaker Vikram Gandhi as he transforms himself into a wise Indian guru, hoping to prove the absurdity of blind faith.
